On nRF51822 baud rate of 921600 b/s can't be set because of bug in serial_api.c:
for-loop needs to go up to 18
```
// serial_baud
// set the baud rate, taking in to account the current SystemFrequency
void serial_baud(serial_t *obj, int baudrate)
{
    if (baudrate<=1200) {
        obj->uart->BAUDRATE = UART_BAUDRATE_BAUDRATE_Baud1200;
        return;
    }

    for (int i = 1; i<18; i++) {
        if (baudrate<acceptedSpeeds[i][0]) {
            obj->uart->BAUDRATE = acceptedSpeeds[i - 1][1];
            return;
        }
    }
    obj->uart->BAUDRATE = UART_BAUDRATE_BAUDRATE_Baud1M;
}
```

